  "title": "Healing Trauma Can Heal Addiction",
  "text": "Healing Trauma Can Heal Addiction\nAddiction and trauma often go hand in hand. Many people who are locked in addiction got there by trying to self-medicate in order to cope with a traumatic event in their lives. Bowen Health licensed social worker and addiction counselor Melanie Strauss talks about how successful treatment involves treating both the trauma as well as the addiction.\nShare this Podcast!",
